{
  "stem": "7093.8",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- I mean, they were constantly in touch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Every week, he went down for the weekend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But anyway, and in the meantime, I, I decided that I must do something about my life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Because I really was very near a complete breakdown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I decided I either get-- I didn't want to live on my own.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Either I find another husband, or I perhaps I try and get a degree.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I, I, I went to lonely clubs every single night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I gave myself two years to find another husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And after one and a half years, I met this husband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And it became very soon we got together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And a year later, I had my divorce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we are now married 20-- well, we were together one year without being married and then 25 years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We just had our silver wedding in October.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And in between them-- and that was an in between-- these two children were born.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And we were grandparents to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we still are.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And my ex-husband is in a-- had breakdowns, one breakdown after the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And he was out in Napsbury Hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "By then, I managed to get him in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "He was better.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I managed to get him in into one of the Jewish refugee homes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "He's in [INAUDIBLE] House, which is one the homes, ref-- Jewish refugee old, old age homes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And I still look after him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And I mean, I still do things for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And, and when he needs something, I do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And they phone me if he needs something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Sometimes, he has a breakdown and has to go out to mental hospital again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And I think that's it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That does bring us up to date, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
